**Example 1: 删除从实例**



Input: 

```
tccli tcr DeleteReplicationInstance --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --RegistryId tcr-12345 \
    --ReplicationRegistryId tcr-12345-5 \
    --ReplicationRegionId 5
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "85d75c18-d98f-4dac-9425-73ea883d2bac"
    }
}
```
